---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import BreakfastCard from '../components/BreakfastCard';

const breakfasts = [
  {
    id: 1,
    name: "Desayuno Romántico",
    description: "Perfecto para sorprender a esa persona especial con pancakes en forma de corazón, frutas y café.",
    price: 24990,
    image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513442542250-854d436a73f2?w=800"
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    name: "Desayuno Cumpleaños",
    description: "Celebra con waffles decorados, huevos revueltos, bacon y jugo natural.",
    price: 29990,
    image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1528207776546-365bb710ee93?w=800"
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    name: "Desayuno Saludable",
    description: "Bowl de açaí, granola casera, frutas frescas y yogurt griego.",
    price: 19990,
    image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511690743698-d9d85f2fbf38?w=800"
  }
];
---

<Layout>
  <div class="relative min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-primary via-secondary to-primary overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/90 via-secondary/80 to-primary/90"></div>
      <img 
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504754524776-8f4f37790ca0?w=1200" 
        alt="Breakfast background" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-24 pb-40">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
          <div class="flex-1 text-left">
            <div class="space-y-4 mb-8 animate-fade-in">
              <div class="flex gap-4 items-center">
                <span class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full text-white text-sm font-medium">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path d="M10.707 2.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 0l-7 7a1 1 0 001.414 1.414L4 10.414V17a1 1 0 001 1h2a1 1 0 001-1v-2a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 001 1h2a1 1 0 001-1v-6.586l.293.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414l-7-7z"/>
                  </svg>
                  Entrega a Domicilio
                </span>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full text-white text-sm font-medium">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path d="M5 4a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v14l-5-2.5L5 18V4z"/>
                  </svg>
                  Personalización Total
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-display font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
              Despierta con<br/>
              <span class="relative">
                <span class="relative z-10">Momentos Mágicos</span>
                <svg class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-full" viewBox="0 0 358 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M2 8.5C2 8.5 89.5 3 178.5 3C267.5 3 356 8.5 356 8.5" stroke="#FFE0B2" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-white/90 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed mb-12">
              Transforma cada mañana en una experiencia única. Nuestros desayunos personalizados llevan la magia directamente a tu puerta, creando recuerdos inolvidables en cada bocado.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6">
              <button 
                onclick="document.getElementById('menu').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'})"
                class="group bg-white text-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-opacity-95 transition transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl inline-flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 relative overflow-hidden"
              >
                <span class="relative z-10">Explorar Menú</span>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
              </button>
              <a 
                href="https://wa.me/+123456789" 
                target="_blank" 
                class="group bg-green-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-green-600 transition transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl inline-flex items-center justify-center space-x-2"
              >
                <span>Contactar</span>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                  <path d="M12.04 2C6.58 2 2.13 6.45 2.13 11.91C2.13 13.66 2.59 15.36 3.45 16.86L2.05 22L7.3 20.62C8.75 21.41 10.38 21.83 12.04 21.83C17.5 21.83 21.95 17.38 21.95 11.92C21.95 9.27 20.92 6.78 19.05 4.91C17.18 3.04 14.69 2 12.04 2M12.05 3.67C14.25 3.67 16.31 4.53 17.87 6.09C19.42 7.65 20.28 9.72 20.28 11.92C20.28 16.46 16.58 20.15 12.04 20.15C10.56 20.15 9.11 19.76 7.85 19L7.55 18.83L4.43 19.65L5.26 16.61L5.06 16.29C4.24 15 3.8 13.47 3.8 11.91C3.81 7.37 7.5 3.67 12.05 3.67M8.53 7.33C8.37 7.33 8.1 7.39 7.87 7.64C7.65 7.89 7 8.5 7 9.71C7 10.93 7.89 12.1 8 12.27C8.14 12.44 9.76 14.94 12.25 16C12.84 16.27 13.3 16.42 13.66 16.53C14.25 16.72 14.79 16.69 15.22 16.63C15.7 16.56 16.68 16.03 16.89 15.45C17.1 14.87 17.1 14.38 17.04 14.27C16.97 14.17 16.81 14.11 16.56 14C16.31 13.86 15.09 13.26 14.87 13.18C14.64 13.1 14.5 13.06 14.31 13.3C14.15 13.55 13.67 14.11 13.53 14.27C13.38 14.44 13.24 14.46 13 14.34C12.74 14.21 11.94 13.95 11 13.11C10.26 12.45 9.77 11.64 9.62 11.39C9.5 11.15 9.61 11 9.73 10.89C9.84 10.78 10 10.6 10.1 10.45C10.23 10.31 10.27 10.2 10.35 10.04C10.43 9.87 10.39 9.73 10.33 9.61C10.27 9.5 9.77 8.26 9.56 7.77C9.36 7.29 9.16 7.35 9 7.34C8.86 7.34 8.7 7.33 8.53 7.33Z"/>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 relative">
            <div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 transform rotate-6">
              <img 
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1533089860892-a7c6f0a88666?w=800" 
                alt="Breakfast 1" 
                class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-2xl transform -rotate-6 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-300"
              />
              <img 
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1496042399014-dc73c4f2bde1?w=800" 
                alt="Breakfast 2" 
                class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-2xl transform translate-y-12 hover:translate-y-10 transition-transform duration-300"
              />
              <img 
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1484723091739-30a097e8f929?w=800" 
                alt="Breakfast 3" 
                class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-2xl transform -translate-y-8 hover:-translate-y-10 transition-transform duration-300"
              />
              <img 
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1455853659719-4b521eebc76d?w=800" 
                alt="Breakfast 4" 
                class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-2xl transform translate-y-4 hover:translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/30 to-secondary/30 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl transform -rotate-6"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1440 320" class="w-full h-auto">
        <path fill="#ffffff" fill-opacity="1" d="M0,160L1440,160L1440,320L0,320Z"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main class="bg-white py-16" id="menu">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-center text-dark mb-4">
        Nuestros Desayunos
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
        Cada desayuno está preparado con ingredientes frescos y puede personalizarse según tus preferencias.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {breakfasts.map(breakfast => (
          <BreakfastCard {...breakfast} client:load />
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>